<div class="policy-wrapper section-padding">
  <h1>{{ section.settings.heading }}</h1>
  <div class="policy-content">
    {{ section.settings.content }}
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Cookie Policy Content",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Policy Title",
      "default": "Cookie Policy"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "content",
      "label": "Policy Content",
      "default": "<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 11 July 2025</p>\n<p>Welcome to Aura Wear. Like most websites, we use cookies to enhance your experience, analyze traffic, and deliver personalized content.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>What Are Cookies?</strong><br>Cookies are small text files stored on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile) when you visit a website. They help the site remember your actions and preferences over time.</li>\n<li><strong>Why We Use Cookies</strong><br>We use cookies for the following purposes:<ul>\n<li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for basic website functionality (e.g., cart, login).</li>\n<li><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how visitors use the site (e.g., Google Analytics).</li>\n<li><strong>Functionality Cookies:</strong> Remember your preferences (e.g., language, currency).</li>\n<li><strong>Marketing Cookies:</strong> Show relevant ads and measure campaign effectiveness.</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Third-Party Cookies</strong><br>Some cookies are set by trusted third parties, such as:<ul>\n<li>Google Analytics – For visitor tracking</li>\n<li>Meta Pixel – For ad performance and targeting</li>\n<li>Shopify – For store functionality and checkout process</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Managing Cookies</strong><br>You can choose to accept or decline cookies at any time by:<ul>\n<li>Adjusting browser settings (to block or delete cookies)</li>\n<li>Clicking “Cookie Settings” on our site (if implemented)</li>\n</ul>Note: Disabling cookies may impact site performance and certain features may not work.</li>\n</ol>"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}

<style>
.policy-wrapper {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 4rem 1rem;
  font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', Arial, sans-serif;
  color: #1D1D1F;
}
.policy-wrapper h1 {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #CDAA7D;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.policy-content {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #222;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(29,29,31,0.08);
  padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
}
.policy-content ul, .policy-content ol {
  margin-left: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.policy-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .policy-wrapper {
    padding: 1.5rem 0.5rem 2rem 0.5rem;
  }
  .policy-content {
    padding: 1rem 0.7rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
}
</style> 